item.title: Moto Traffic
item.description: During the game Moto simulator 3d you have to ride a very fast vehicle. You have a great motorcycle at your disposal, and you can ride it anywhere and any way you like. At the bottom of the screen is a speedometer, thanks to which you can always estimate your own speed.
